## 🔧 配置项

### COS 配置（⚠️ 关键）
```json
{
  "bucket": "claw-1301484442",
  "region": "ap-shanghai",
  "secret_id": "AKIDWYbw77uSntsgHeokDSTItITQAi20jLlz",
  "secret_key": "570JTPAl8IFzaxNgokU0Lgp8IG2d1DE1",
  "cos_path": "reports/issue_analysis/",
  "content_type": "text/html; charset=utf-8",
  "content_disposition": "inline",
  "cache_control": "no-cache"
}
```

**⚠️ 关键配置说明**:
- `content_type`: 必须是 `text/html; charset=utf-8`，确保浏览器识别为 HTML
- `content_disposition`: 必须是 `inline`，确保在浏览器打开而不是下载
- `cache_control`: 设置为 `no-cache`，确保看到最新数据

### 报告配置
```json
{
  "chart_library": "chart.js@4.4.0",
  "theme_color": "#667eea",
  "font_family": "-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, PingFang SC",
  "output_format": "html",
  "auto_upload": true
}
```

### 告警规则
